# GitHub Copilot Instructions

Use this repository's spec-driven workflow as the default operating model.

## Required Entry Points

- Start new non-trivial work from `{{BRIEF_ARTIFACT}}` using the brief workflow.
- Do not skip directly to implementation when the feature still needs clarification.
- Use the matching workflow process only after the brief slug is approved.

## Source Of Truth

- `workflow-pack.json`
- `.workflow-pack/manifest.json`
- `AGENTS.md`
- `CLAUDE.md`

## Required Behavior

- Respect the selected profile: `{{PROFILE_NAME}}`.
- Respect the configured add-ons and quality gates.
- Do not overwrite or revert another collaborator's work without explicit approval.
- Keep shared artifacts updated before claiming completion.
- Use the generated custom agents in `.github/agents/` for the brief and workflow flows when appropriate.
